{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165620/extras/STEAMWatch_Learn.png?t=1736774425\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165620/extras/BSWatch_LearnGIF.gif?t=1736774425\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>How well do you know your planet and the universe beyond?</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Let\u2019s put your knowledge to the test! Embark on an exciting journey filled with captivating trivia, stunning visuals, and surprising discoveries!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Whether you're exploring Earth's wonders, unlocking secrets of the cosmos, or challenging friends and family, this game offers endless opportunities to learn and have fun. Are you ready to prove your skills and claim the title of ultimate quiz champion?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165620/extras/STEAMPlayWithFriends.png?t=1736774425\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165620/extras/BSMultiGIF.gif?t=1736774425\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Challenge yourself with 4 unique modes:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Watch &amp; Learn</strong> - More of a visual learner? Put your memory to the test with questions about the video you just watched!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Campaign</strong> - Explore the regions of our planet, complete exciting chapters, and earn well-deserved medals!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Quick Play</strong> - Select the difficulty, take your time, and enjoy an awesome quiz on any topic you choose!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Tournament</strong> - Want to showcase what you learned? Compete with your friends or family for the title of Quiz Master!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Features:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Over 2000 questions to test your knowledge! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Local multiplayer mode for up to 4 players! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">4 diverse gameplay modes! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Quizpedia with all the information you need </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Engaging educational videos! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Eye-catching visuals</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Discover new facts about the world and the vast universe beyond!</p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Third time in a row","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3165620/3d9eba6fdd9cf7c8aab3888b4793267af1e3e509.jpg"},{"name":"Great minds think alike","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3165620/91edf85e200c03a0aedb4cfb7e4cd5b095d90a9c.jpg"},{"name":"No man left behind","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3165620/bd7572f3d9917cd0ebf1d93c4a14b7fa6063f56d.jpg"},{"name":"Knowledge master","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3165620/d2aa73f7eff2899111bfac57ad7f6e4e6fcc60aa.jpg"},{"name":"Speed master","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3165620/b12d74e4ff98cfe9ae32061b6f2469192b1e32cc.jpg"},{"name":"Quiz champion","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3165620/ec82bc1d3f364c44d7e80d800b25b7bae9bd2b0c.jpg"},{"name":"That was quick","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3165620/d2a4fdf4dfcc10dc27def6e0920619f5c7b7af65.jpg"},{"name":"One 